  "body": "this is a potential [volunteer pickup task](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/labels/I)\r\n\r\nsnapshot is defined as a journal in with only 'up' event (at most one per node or connection)\r\nYou create a snapshot from a running simulation by iterating trough events backwards, and remember the last state or each node and connection in a map. \r\nThen iterate through the map and include the 'up' events only.\r\nhttps://github.com/ethersphere/go-ethereum/blob/whisper/p2p/simulations/journal.go#L94\r\n",
